g":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750df1dc46338f6d8a843dbde486ddc2e08493e1","tid":145584,"uid":76605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"食神 燉奶佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664d14e9ccd81a60ce99c067614f408455a39b48","tid":145584,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食神 燉奶佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食神下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燉奶佬嗰喱腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但近年越來越少牛腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b557532fb3801b8667c238a92e9d35482aa5cf","tid":145584,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8262575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8262575.jpg&h=28a16e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平民美食講，整體中上，係抵屌既<br />\n<br />\n不過目測係食豬扒飯多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780c4c28368e17febdaa964d51e9e920d2664ba0","tid":145584,"uid":73275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食神 燉奶佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩放監出黎? 食神收左皮好耐啦<br />\n<br />\n樓上有ching講左金城肉餅飯<br />\n林園啲香茅豬扒同雞翼都好食<br />\n<br />\n顯徑百味村車仔麵<br />\n<br />\n大圍積信街 陳記茶餐廳<br />\n洋蔥汁同蒜蓉汁<br />\n要睇個日餐牌有無 因為真係用蒜蓉同洋蔥開 唔似其他垃圾茶記用茄汁溝鳩埋就算"},{"pid":"6a18d0e55