0800c17c21dc1c3fe56e245a663e6a6789535794","tid":145584,"uid":12006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"金城係食辣菜莆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b27e6d38ec14c7df4fda9381a0266d44b401f41","tid":145584,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:20:14.000Z","msg":"竟然有人推食神，D叉燒臭既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58cf06d32380b3f8b4301187cc21bb5acb55052","tid":145584,"uid":73275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食神 燉奶佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩放監出黎? 食神收左皮好耐啦<br />\n<br />\n樓上有ching講左金城肉餅飯<br />\n林園啲香茅豬扒同雞翼都好食<br />\n<br />\n顯徑百味村車仔麵<br />\n<br />\n大圍積信街 陳記茶餐廳<br />\n洋蔥汁同蒜蓉汁<br />\n要睇個日餐牌有無 因為真係用蒜蓉同洋蔥開 唔似其他垃圾茶記用茄汁溝鳩埋就算</blockquote><br />\n陳記未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲汁點配最好食？</blockquote><br />\n平時都係食雞扒雙腸飯豉油汁<br />\n見到個日餐牌有寫蒜蓉或者洋蔥汁就雞扒雙腸飯跟個汁。唔係成日有 亦都唔知邊日會有 睇個四眼仔心情 賣完即止"},{"pid":"4de2f107d7a06fe01dd37400ec817e1a7a851143","tid":145584,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金城係食辣菜莆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識食呀! <br />\n我住香港區，都好多時特登去食"},{"pid":"e0a5d6d1bde894e9aea044455e64d47f94d7c5ed","tid":145584,"uid":19272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金城係食辣菜莆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識食呀! <br />\n我住香港區，都好多時特登去食</blockquote><br />\n呢個堅爽，我會買返屋企食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d89da02c99ead69639